    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "2019 sedan in poor condition. The exterior has noticeable scratches, dents, and rust in multiple areas. The interior shows significant wear \u2014 upholstery is damaged, trim pieces are worn or broken, and some components are not functioning properly. Mechanically, the car has issues that will likely require attention. Best suited for buyers comfortable with a project vehicle or those looking for parts.",
